&lt;li&gt;A collaborative team player who enjoys developing and refining program strategies—such as learner engagement tactics, career readiness resources, and employer-aligned preparation—to ensure participant success across diverse backgrounds and experience levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly organized with strong program and project management skills, able to coordinate across stakeholders (learners, instructors, employers, internal teams) while keeping long-term program goals—such as job placement, learner skill mastery, and stakeholder satisfaction—front and center.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
