&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to work in a fast-paced environment where your output has a direct impact on the company&#39;s growth. If you are a driven and results-oriented senior sales professional, we encourage you to apply for this exciting opportunity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will report directly to the Senior Vice President of Strategic Growth and offers a combination of base salary and variable compensation.&lt;/p&gt;
